snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedBackslashEscape

client = AsyncSeedBackslashEscape(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.user.get(
        id="id",
        domain="domain",
    )


asyncio.run(main())
